Keamogetse Sadie Kenosi (amụrụ na 17 Jenụwarị na afo 1997) bụ onye na-akụ ọkpọ na Botswana. O sonyere na asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị na afọ 2020 Summer Olympics. Karriss Artingstall nke Great Britain meriri ya na agba nke mbụ
Na mbụ ọ bụ onye na-egwu netball, Kenosi malitere ịkụ ọkpọ na afọ 2015
O sonyere na afọ 2019 World Championships wee merie ọla edo na afọ 2019 African Games.
